author: Kendall Moore
text:
Pt. II …happened last night! Before I sign off, to never speak on this incident again, let me just ask this:

If this had happened at the BET awards  or another predominantly Black event, would people make this much fuss about it?

author: Kendall Moore
text: I don’t usually tweet, but I’m just burnt out over all this Will Smith “press”. There are so many important things going on in the world, and yet we’re focusing on a man defending his wife. Right or wrong, it’s not the worst thing in the world, it wasn’t even the worst thing…
